## Operator review checklist before send

- [ ] Recipient email is correct AIMS contact per `aims-routing-map.md`
- [ ] Subject line follows `DRAFT for your approval - <Customer> (<Contact>): <Topic>` pattern
- [ ] Attachment path resolves and the PDF is the right version
- [ ] All `{{HIGHLIGHT_N}}` placeholders replaced with real values
- [ ] No `{{PLACEHOLDER}}` tokens remain
- [ ] Estimated value matches the proposal's §8 Payment Terms section
- [ ] CC list is right (AIMS senior + SRE internal owner — not end-customer at this stage)
- [ ] Length 100–180 words

**Approved by**: ______________ **Date**: __________

